## Step 3: Disassemble `verify_user_name`

```
(gdb) disas verify_user_name
(gdb) x/s 0x80486a8
0x80486a8: "dat_wil"
```

The function compares the first 7 bytes of the global buffer `a_user_name` against `"dat_wil"` using `repz cmpsb`. The expected username is **`dat_wil`**.

